| File | Size | Lines | Purpose |
|------|------|-------|---------|
| plugin.cpp | 401 KB | ~9500 | Main visualization logic |
| milkdropfs.cpp | 190 KB | ~3000 | Preset/filesystem system |
| pluginshell.cpp | 124 KB | ~2000 | Plugin shell/Winamp integration |
| state.cpp | 83 KB | ~2000 | State management |
| dxcontext.cpp | 47 KB | ~1500 | DirectX rendering |
| fft.cpp | 8.5 KB | ~220 | **FFT CORE** |
| fft.h | 4.3 KB | ~80 | **FFT HEADER** |
| **TOTAL** | **~1.9 MB** | **~28k lines** | |

### Key Numbers

- **Architecture**: Plugin shell + 6 major modules
- **FFT Butterflies**: ~10,240 per frame
- **Sample Rate**: 44.1 kHz (must handle 192kHz in Rust!)
- **Frame Size**: 576 samples = 13.06ms @ 44.1kHz
- **FFT Output Bins**: 512 (frequency domain)
- **Preset Variables**: 6 audio-reactive (bass/mid/treb × 2)
- **Precomputed Tables**: 4 tables, ~4KB total
- **Memory per FFT**: ~8KB

