| Smoothing | 0.05ms | 0.1ms | Temporal filtering |
| Preset Eval | 0.5ms | 1.0ms | Expression VM |
| Rendering | 10ms | 16ms | 60 FPS target |
| **Total** | **11.15ms** | **18.3ms** | Real-time capable |

