## 4. Feature Flags

### 4.1 Main Library (`milkdropper`)

```toml
[features]
default = ["wgpu-render", "simd"]

# Rendering backends
wgpu-render = ["milkdropper-render/wgpu-backend"]
software-render = ["milkdropper-render/software-backend"]

# Audio optimizations
